name: 26.4.86 (04/x)
description: 35 years ago, the major nuclear disaster in history occurred. It was the explosion of reactor No.4 in the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant. That catastrophe took many lives and caused irreparable damage to the environment. The consequences of that explosion are still in evidence. The humankind shall not forget about this to make sure that the history will not repeat itself in the future.      In memory of the people who died and suffered in the result of Chernobyl disaster. 26.04.1986
